	(340,1,'2014-09-05 14:30:38','2014-09-05 14:30:38','[quote]Soco stands for Southern Contemporary. Its a new and adventurous\r\nculinary approach to dishes that we have all come to know and love. At\r\nSoco we are focused on true Southern hospitality, and we are committed\r\nto overall excellence.[quote-citation][quote-author]Greg Richie[/quote-author] Executive Chef/Partner[/quote-citation][/quote]\r\n\r\n[divider][/divider]\r\n\r\n[section-heading]Our Story[/section-heading]\r\n[column-wrap][column size=\"one-half\"]\r\n\r\nFrom the windows of Soco’s cozy dining room to the patio overlooking the lively corner of Central and Summerlin, Soco unites the essence of true Southern hospitality with the charm of the Thornton Park neighborhood.\r\n\r\nThe grand window into our kitchen allows guests to watch our talented chefs create their carefully constructed dishes, just as you would peek into you own kitchen and watch your favorite home-cooked meals being prepared. At the bar, neighbors and friends greet each other over a uniquely crafted cocktail or snifter of bourbon from Soco’s extensive reserve list.\r\n\r\nSoco’s thoughtfully sourced cuisine, crafted cocktails and Southern hospitality make it the perfect dining experience for your most special occasion celebrations, or every day fine dining with your friends and neighbors.[/column]\r\n\r\n[column size=\"one-half\"]\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://dev.socothorntonpark.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/OysterDish.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-339\" src=\"http://dev.socothorntonpark.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/OysterDish-300x199.jpg\" alt=\"OysterDish\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" /></a>\r\n\r\n[/column][/column-wrap]','About','','inherit','open','open','','189-revision-v1','','','2014-09-05 14:30:38','2014-09-05 14:30:38','',189,'http://dev.socothorntonpark.com/189-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
