y list. Our semi-private room is the ideal downtown location for a business dinner, special event or group function.\r\n\r\n[section-heading]Our Group[/section-heading]\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-673\" style=\"width: 190px !important; height: 109px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\" src=\"http://dev.socothorntonpark.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/TPRG-logo.png\" alt=\"TPRG-logo\" width=\"190\" height=\"109\" />\r\n\r\nSoco is owned and operated by the <a href=\"http://www.thorntonparkrg.com\">Thornton Park Restaurant Group</a>. We are proud to be a local and independent ownership group. Our sister restaurant is <a href=\"http://www.cityfishorlando.com\">Cityfish</a>, located a few doors down from Soco at 617 East Central Boulevard. TPRG is developing a new concept for the former Urban Rethink Bookstore space at 625 East Central Boulevard, next door to Soco. For more information, please visit:\r\n\r\n[section-heading]Our Friends[/section-heading]\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"bullets\">\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.thorntonparkdistrict.com\" target=\"_blank\">Thornton Park District</a><br /><span style=\"font-size: 12px; display: block; position: relative; margin-top: -4px; margin-bottom: 5px;\">- Our community</span></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.thegravitycompany.com\" target=\"_blank\">The Gravity Company</a><br /><span style=\"font-size: 12px; display: block; position: relative; margin-top: -4px; margin-bottom: 5px;\">- Our designers</span></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.sunshineplate.org\" target=\"_blank\">Sunshine Plate Coalition</a><br /><span style=\"font-size: 12px; display: block; position: relative; margin-top: -4px; margin-bottom: 5px;\">- Greater Orlando food leaders alliance</span></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.southernfoodways.org\" target=\"_blank\">Southern Foodways Alliance</a><br /><span style=\"font-size: 12px; display: block; position: relative; margin-top: -4px; margin-bottom: 5px;\">- Regional alliance celebrati